'''Alkin''' deg [[takrura tagmant|tekrura tagmant]] d [[hidṛukaṛbun|ahidṛukaṛbun]] [[aseklu|ur nettwaseṛwu]], Dges ma drus yiwet n [[turza tattekkant|turza]] (ttwaqqna) timisint gar n sin n [[abelkim|ibelkimen]] n [[Akaṛbun|ukaṛbun]].
Dɣa tilkinin tifrarin ilan (yesɛan) yiwet n turza tusligt gellunt-d s [[tazrart tasnulut]] u tilkinin lant (sɛant) [[taftart takrurant]] tamatant '''C<sub>n</sub>H<sub>2n</sub>'''.

Tilkinin tifrarin yakk d win yettusemman [[itilin]], Maca isem-is deg [[tiddukla tagreɣlant i tekrura tuzdigt d tusnist|tdukla tagreɣlant i tekrura tuzdigt d tusnist IUPAC]] d ''itin''

